author: Warhammer
description:
Begin with Imperial Fist over white for a hot magma-core!
Next, grab Magmadroth Flame and some sponge in a tube.
Start dabbing it onto the outer edges for an intense, glowing orange, Leaving some yellow on show
Don't be afraid if it's a bit messy, this will all come together at the end!
Sponge Blood Angels Red, followed by Flesh Tearers Red, focusing on the tips and outer edges for a deep, molten red feel.
Finishing with Black Legion along the very edge for a - charred look.
